OL,3,C'I have to see my dad's killer in
OL,4,CTesco' - son of man killed in one-
OL,5,Cpunch attack
OL,7,FThe son of a man killed in a one-punch
OL,8,Fattack is urging people to walk away
OL,9,Fwhenever they feel angry.
OL,11,FFather-of-three Adrian Cooksey was
OL,12,Fkilled by Richard Elmes - a man who
OL,13,Fwas supposed to be his best friend -
OL,14,Fwhile on a night out in Wiltshire in
OL,15,F2009.
OL,17,FThe pair had been out drinking with
OL,18,Fold school friends before Adrian was
OL,19,Ffound on a pavement in Melksham. He'd
OL,20,Fbeen left alone by the roadside to die.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
