OL,7,FHe said: "There was no-one with him
OL,8,Fwhen he was found.
OL,10,F"I think people in Wiltshire were a
OL,11,Fbit stumped as to what had happened.
OL,12,FThe police were stumped."
OL,14,FWiltshire Police arrested student
OL,15,FThomas Minshull, who had been in the
OL,16,Farea at the time. He was put on trial
OL,17,Ffor manslaughter where Adrian's real
OL,18,Fkiller - Elmes - gave evidence against
OL,19,Fhim.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
