OL,4,CTesco' - son of man killed in one-
OL,5,Cpunch attack
OL,7,FWiltshire Police eventually turned
OL,8,Ftheir attention to Elmes, bugging his
OL,9,Fcar and overhearing a conversation
OL,10,Fwith his wife where he admitted
OL,11,F"telling porkies".
OL,13,FThree years after Adrian's death,
OL,14,FElmes admitted perjury but denied
OL,15,Fmanslaughter.
OL,17,FHe was convicted by a jury who heard
OL,18,Fthe pair had argued over an affair
OL,19,FElmes had with a married woman years
OL,20,Fbefore.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
