OL,3,C'I have to see my dad's killer in
OL,4,CTesco' - son of man killed in one-
OL,5,Cpunch attack
OL,7,FElmes was jailed for six years in 2012
OL,8,Fand is now a free man.
OL,10,F"We weren't told when he was
OL,11,Freleased," Adam said. "The first time
OL,12,FI came across him was in a Tesco
OL,13,FExpress in 2016.
OL,15,F"I was on my way out for a night out."
OL,17,FAs part of One Punch Awareness Week,
OL,18,FAdam is urging people to walk away
OL,19,Fwhen they feel anger coming over them.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
