OL,3,C'I have to see my dad's killer in
OL,4,CTesco' - son of man killed in one-
OL,5,Cpunch attack
OL,7,F"I always have it in the back of my
OL,8,Fmind (that I could see Elmes), I have
OL,9,Fto be prepared to walk away. You've
OL,10,Fgot to walk away."
OL,12,FHe added: "Everyone as a youngster has
OL,13,Fan ego. But you've got to let it go.
OL,14,FThe devastation it can leave never
OL,15,Fgoes away."
